1. Build Instructions:
======================

Contents:
---------
1.1 The Server
1.2 The NCurses Client
1.3 The Random AI
1.4 The pyQt4 Client

1.1 The Server
--------------
Requirements: glibc
Resulting executables: server
Procedure:
    cd servex/
    make

1.2 The NCurses Client
----------------------
Requirements: glibc, ncurses headers (ncurses-dev)
Resulting executables: client, client.db
Procedure:
    cd clientex/
    make

1.3 The Random AI
-----------------
Requirements: glibc, completed client build
Resulting executables: random
Procedure:
    cd clientex/ai/random/
    make

1.4 The pyQt4 Client
--------------------
Requirements: python, pyqt4 (python-qt4)
Resulting executables: client.py
Procedure:
    cd pyqt/
    chmod +x client.py
